www-subtext: Pezani mayankho otseguka okwana 1.2 miliyoni kudzera pa bolodi lolumikizanali, chida chapadera chomwe chimalumikiza mawu a amayi ndi atsikana ndi kuthekera kosawerengeka kwa kusanthula kwa digito.
midwives-voices-subtext: Tinafunsa azamba padziko lonse funso lakuti: “Kodi mumafuna chiyani kwambiri pa ntchito yanu monga mzamba?”
pmnch-subtext: Takulandirani ku Dashboard ya "Zomwe Achinyamata Amafuna"! Chida chothandizirachi chimapereka chithunzithunzi cha mayankho ndi zidziwitso zomwe tikusonkhanitsa kuchokera kwa achinyamata azaka zapakati pa 10-24 padziko lonse lapansi. Mfundo yaikulu ya ntchitoyi ndi funso lotseguka: "Kuti ndikhale ndi moyo wabwino, ndikufuna ...". Achinyamata ochokera padziko lonse lapansi akhala akuyankha izi, kutipatsa chidziwitso chapadera pa zosowa zawo, ziyembekezo, ndi zokhumba zawo. Onani zambiri, pezani nkhani za manambala, ndikugwirizana nafe kukulitsa mawu a achinyamata 1.8 biliyoni padziko lonse lapansi. Kuti mudziwe zambiri za kampeniyi, pitani ku http://www.1point8.org.
to-protect-anonymity: Pofuna kuteteza kuti anthu asadziwike, ena omwe anafunsidwa achotsedwa pa bolodi ili.
